From: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
Date: Thu, 25 Apr 2019 14:40:51 +0700
Subject: [PATCH 064/326] arm64: defconfig: enable PWM based Backlight in RZ/G2
 SoC

This patch enables config for support PWM based Backlight
in RZ/G2 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Hien Huynh <hien.huynh.px@renesas.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/defconfig | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig b/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
index 664111b..d478044 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
@@ -463,7 +463,7 @@ CONFIG_DRM_DW_HDMI=y
 CONFIG_FB=y
 CONFIG_FB_ARMCLCD=y
 CONFIG_BACKLIGHT_GENERIC=m
-CONFIG_BACKLIGHT_PWM=m
+CONFIG_BACKLIGHT_PWM=y
 CONFIG_BACKLIGHT_LP855X=m
 CONFIG_LOGO=y
 # CONFIG_LOGO_LINUX_MONO is not set
